# 📘 Month 1: Foundations of Red Hat Linux

Welcome to Month 1 of my RHCSA journey! This chapter is focused on the **core fundamentals** — everything from installation, users, navigation, permissions, and system basics. These are the building blocks I’ll need before diving into more advanced sysadmin tasks.

